Project Description

This project explores the use of different AI tools such as ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, and Claude to generate professional content using prompts.
The main objective was to understand how different Large Language Models respond to the same instructions and how prompt engineering can improve the quality of the output.

In this project, prompts were used to generate a professional email invitation for a workshop titled Future of Generative AI (FGAI). 
Persona prompting was applied to make the AI respond like a research assistant or event coordinator.

An event poster was generated using **DALL-E Image Creator**, and a short promotional video suitable for social media was created using **Fliki.ai and Kaleido.ai**.
These tools demonstrate how generative AI can assist in content creation, marketing, and communication.

Overall, this project helped in gaining hands-on experience with multiple AI platforms, refining prompts, and generating text, image, and video content using AI technologies.
